Package: NetworkEnvGradGeneration
Type: Package
Title: Generate networks along environmental gradient
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rémi Legrand
Maintainer: Rémi Legrand <remi.legrand38@gmail.com>
Description: Generate random networks along an environmental gradient. To do so:
    - Generate random niches for each species uniformly distributed along this gradient.
    - Induce abundances from it.
    - Make trait matching.
    - Generate a theoretical interaction matrix.
    - Sample using multinomial.
